{"tid":652927,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 匯豐宣佈加息","createTime":"2018-05-04T08:45:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-04T10:22:56.000Z","uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b9271cd2f25a8aa8baf206e93dd24fffb2e6e8fb","tid":652927,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/04/164511_3063a09913a60c01094bbabe46ea7b14.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F04%2F164511_3063a09913a60c01094bbabe46ea7b14.png&h=d7dc7de3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a35951a5dec1052a69682d9c26405e3e47a22ebf","tid":652927,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:47:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"104b59e0ffc8e23a02b8ff39ed223cde03136fa9","tid":652927,"uid":102096,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:47:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f8bcf6b44e752d027a27c067b0c63169b285162e","tid":652927,"uid":33357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:48:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"971f9453b6d0fb502d73a3e21d2cd7c0826e3a9e","tid":652927,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:49:32.000Z","msg":"匯豐調高美元存款利息至0.1厘 9年來首次 (16:01)<br />\n<br />\n文章日期：2018年5月4日<br />\n<br />\n匯控（0005）行政總裁范寧在分析員會議上透露，匯豐在香港是首家銀行把儲蓄存款戶口利息由0.0001％升至0.1％，是9年來首次調升，雖然非重大改變，但也是一個廣泛的訊號（broad signal），反映銀行要與客戶分享利息上升的好處，他相信匯豐要帶頭去調升儲蓄存款利息。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，范寧所指的利息上調，只限於在香港的美元儲蓄存款戶口，而非港元戶口。昨日集團已公布，港元的儲蓄存款戶口利率，維持不變，最高為0.001％。<br />\n<br />\n不少分析員均追問存款利息上升，對集團的息差會否帶來壓力，集團財務總監Iain Mackay表示，淨息差仍將是擴闊趨勢，但存款市場的競爭確實愈來愈大，尤其在香港及其他亞洲地區，他相信未來市場會變得更有趣，而集團的目標是繼續保持龐大的流動性。<br />\n<br />\n集團其後發出新聞稿，表示由今日起，把美元儲蓄存款戶口利率調升至0.1％，適用於結餘1000美元及以上的戶口。該行對上一次調整美元儲蓄存款戶口利率為2009年5月底，當時減息0.9點子。<br />\n<br />\n記者：廖毅然"},{"pid":"83edeb5bf0f8779eb61503d895d73d6b1e5cbed8","tid":652927,"uid":102198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:50:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6073a5c116088ec3b28d2c3cc0e55ad76079dfe1","tid":652927,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T08:53:33.000Z","msg":"大貓銀行係咪收左美帝錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6985e768e4cf4bc38b6d018d3f0731670bbe0b77","tid":652927,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T09:43:15.000Z","msg":"只限於在香港的美元儲蓄存款戶口"},{"pid":"f3d0a12e49587e7c3a1835e36fd07e799e56886a","tid":652927,"uid":1082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T09:45:40.000Z","msg":"轉晒做美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"725355d70727e0303713a7c53c667911cf5a34d5","tid":652927,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T09:50:01.000Z","msg":"沽港紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"370440958eeb19a59fdb63baa0ce90f621d5d47e","tid":652927,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T09:51:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6496a18e2d60072e612e3137a4486f4a450bb2c8","tid":652927,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T10:01:32.000Z","msg":"升！"},{"pid":"72466d0b7bfb29cf42f88e71bd4a2ffc505539af","tid":652927,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T10:02:57.000Z","msg":"丁屎咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ...."},{"pid":"5b2d861463796e54932e386c8194a77f88f95a69","tid":652927,"uid":59567,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-04T10:22:56.000Z","msg":"一次加一百倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n樓爆啦世界未日"}]}